# EURONAVAL 2022

Greek French Forum - Maritime and Naval Cooperation

GICAN organized a distinguished event on franco-greek cooperation in coordination with its Greek partner SEKPY and the support of the CCI France Grèce.

![](/static/media/uploads/blog/1666272489911.jpg)

This one-day event included lectures and two round-tables.

First round-table: Naval Cooperation, a positive state of play and commitment to continue.

Second round-table: Greece and France, two maritime countries, that promote the security and development at sea.

![](/static/media/uploads/blog/1666272487656.jpg)

CENSUS successfully participated in the second-round table, titled **"Opportunities for securing sustainable maritime activities"**, promoting the security and development of activities at sea.
